    {
      "id": "PopularPost77003",
      "post_content": "Strictly better than [Mons's Goblin Raiders](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mons's Goblin Raiders), Goblin Balloon Brigade is a decent one-drop for red. With [Goblin King](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin King) in play, these make for decent attackers. In a pinch, they make for a great chump blocker for your opponent's [Serra Angel](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serra Angel) or [Shivan Dragon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shivan Dragon).",
      "posted_by": "Eppek_the_Goblin",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost77003\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Strictly better than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mons's Goblin Raiders\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mons's Goblin Raiders\">Mons's Goblin Raiders</a>, Goblin Balloon Brigade is a decent one-drop for red.  With <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Goblin King\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Goblin King\">Goblin King</a> in play, these make for decent attackers.  In a pinch, they make for a great chump blocker for your opponent's <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Serra Angel\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serra Angel\">Serra Angel</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Shivan Dragon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shivan Dragon\">Shivan Dragon</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '77003'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy525\">Eppek_the_Goblin</span>\r\n                                (6/1/2010 9:28:34 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainCont