      "id": "PopularPost187741",
      "post_content": "Not strictly better than Mons's Goblin Raiders; you might want to use it in a deck with [Muraganda Petroglyphs](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Muraganda Petroglyphs).   \n  \nIt's a good card though, because red has very few little fliers and even fewer that can block. And it's a goblin to top it off.",
